'''Kuat Photonics''' was a privately-owned [[Kuati/Legends|Kuati]] endeavor. During the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]], their [[Starship/Legends|ships]] were tracked by [[Talon Karrde]] and found to be carrying supplies for the [[Peace Brigade]]. They were thought to be sponsored by [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] [[Senator/Legends|senator]] [[Viqi Shesh]], although even [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] was unable to find to evidence to such a partnership.

